from collections import Counter

def find_kth_lexicographic_pair(n, k, arr):
    c = list(Counter(arr).items())
    c.sort()
    s = 1
    fi = 0
    i = 0
    while i < len(c):
        s += c[i][1] * n
        if s >= k:
            fi = i
            k -= s - c[i][1] * n
            break
        i += 1
    si = 0
    i = 0
    s = 0
    while i < len(c):
        s += c[i][1] * c[fi][1]
        if s >= k:
            si = i
            break
        i += 1
    return (c[fi][0], c[si][0])
